profile:
As a family owned business, In The Back Yard Limited brings 40 years of combined experience in building custom wood solutions that offers everything from basic garden sheds and structures to cottage bunkies and garages! We have been located in the Stoney Creek, Ontario area for the past 5 years and service the entire Southern Ontario region including the GTA area.  From design, to build to installation, we see the job from beginning to end.

All our installations include a block and gravel foundation, shingles, one single door or double door (depending on the style of shed) and 1 window. For the do-it-your self customer, each of our standard sheds can be purchased as a kit. Quality craftsmanship, affordability and customer satisfaction is not just what we provide, it's what we guarantee. Give us a call at 905-664-4224 and together we can turn your backyard structure design ideas into reality. It is not only the quality of our products & services that make us successful, it is how we make you feel!  

We are Baeumler Approved.
products: Wooden custom sheds and stand-alone garages.
services: Design, build, deliver and install wooden sheds and stand-alone garages.
specialities: We specialize in custom designing sheds that meet your requirements.  If not sure, we can certainly help give you ideas.
payment_method: Credit Card, Debit Card, Cheque, Cash
